Class FixedSizedObjectPool<T>

    public class FixedSizedObjectPool<T>
extends Object
implements org.apache.hadoop.hive.common.Pool<T>
    Simple object pool of limited size. Implemented as a lock-free ring buffer; may fail to produce items if there are too many concurrent users.
